metadata.name: Mr C.O.Rona #1
metadata.description: Current population of the earth is nearly 8 Billion people, and in the past 2 1/2 years every single one of us, have been directly or indirectly affected by Mr C.O.Rona wether you were in the deserts of Africa, the highland Peaks of Asia, the tropics of South America or the Villages and cities all over the planet. Wether you are Believer or a sceptic of this mad pandemic it has divided society in a negative way! Therefore Mr C.O. Rona has risen in all his splendour and glory to unite us all and to see who were you and where you were all in this madness. Lets begin the healing and unity of society with the help of Mr Rona.
